Bitcoin campfire version1.08 - Release date: 13 October 2020
FPS test at spawn: PC:91-91 | Laptop:74-53 | Quest:67-44

Changes:
- Added menus:
      - World settings (campfire - snow - hide pens - clear pens - postprocessing - players shadows)
      - Chess settings (start a new game - hide pieces - debug pieces - reset board - light)

- Added hill & wizard house (exterior only) - optimized materials for quest.
- Added "reset board" button to the chess board with others debug stuff.
- Added snow, toggle from the World settings menu.
- Added a second working bow.
- Added seats on top of the big Bitcoin
- Added props: direction - lamps - barrier and others.

- Moved archery target, now on by default.
- Moved chess board, now on by default.
- Modified mirror
- Modified spawn point
- Modified post-processing settings: bloom and post exposure
- Rebaked everything with better settings.
- Fixed colliders under the bridge
- Fixed chair selector


